data.description: Beautiful All Brick Ranch 3 bedrooms and 2 baths with large open floor plan that backs up to Whiteside ball fields. Wonderful Wood burning fireplace in Living room. Large Kitchen/Dining combo w/solid wood Schmidt Cabinetry (Locally Made). Beautiful laminate flooring and updated bathrooms. Bedrooms are good sized. Large open garage has a Kevlar Storm room and laundry area with Newer High efficiency Furnace and Hot water heater. All Windows are thermal tilt in windows. Nice 2 story shed in rear yard and very large composite deck with 6 ft Aluminum Fence. Landscaped nicely around home but always room to add your own touches. Custom insulated garage door with newer opener. Curb appeal is phenomenal and parking is great. Nice central vac system but buyer will need to get new hose accessories. SELLER SAYS BRING OFFER
